  "siteName": "阿真Irene",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div style=\"font-weight:400;padding-left:10px;font-size:16px;line-height:2;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;padding-right:10px;text-align:justify;\">\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;border-radius: 8px;overflow: hidden;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4185185185185185\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=19d5f05f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FHibrYDJehdiacTWt7rC3ZGvqbS2Vc7Vib7ibib5p37mqvw0jq0bNsOe1fc2Tc8RhqKRVVy8icNpiaMHEGmGfJBDWuxewA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">嗨大家好！我是阿真！这将是我今年最后一次说这句话，因为下次说这句话将会是2026年了哈哈哈。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">首先想表达感谢，感谢放在最前面，因为朋友们对我真的很重要，感恩！</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">2025年，感谢所有朋友们的一路陪伴，是mini博主到little博主的进步！你们的认可和鼓励，让我更有动力持续输出，表达更清晰了，更有自信了，内核也更稳了。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">然后要360度托马斯全旋感谢AI顶流博主</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 92, 212);box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">@数字生命卡兹克</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，如果不是因为他转载了我的文章，我也许还是会走到大家面前，但绝不可能这么快，伯乐之恩，永远铭记在心。卡老师真的是非常真诚也非常努力的人，从他那里我学到了不忘初心，学到了勇于表达，学到了坚持的力量。2025年至少有一半的时间他都在熬夜产出，新的一年希望他也多多保重身体少熬夜，焦虑少一点快乐多一点，付出都有回报。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;border-radius: 8px;overflow: hidden;box-shadow: rgb(241, 240, 253) 3px 3px 3px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6712962962962963\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=60e0282e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FHibrYDJehdiacTWt7rC3ZGvqbS2Vc7Vib7ibQJxG3BfYwIyH00dfNm8CLibejJdz9P1YguHZEWGsBOaoIW9TZbRTkQg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;text-align: center;-webkit-box-reflect: below -1px -webkit-linear-gradient(top, transparent, transparent 93%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8));box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;padding: 2px;border-radius: 4px;margin-top: 0.8em;background-image: linear-gradient(135deg, rgb(212, 141, 247) 0%, rgb(92, 79, 235) 80%);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"border:1px dashed rgba(255, 255, 255, 0);border-radius:4px;padding:0px 15px;font-size:24px;line-height:1.6;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">今年的小结</span></strong></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">今年一共写了116篇公众号原创内容。</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 2;font-style: normal;text-align: justify;font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;color: rgb(102, 92, 212);box-sizing: border-box;\">现在看有部分内容可能有点过时了，但是有的思路可能还可以参考。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 2;font-style: normal;text-align: justify;font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;color: rgb(102, 92, 212);box-sizing: border-box;\">个人觉得自己最好的5篇内容🔽</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link mp_article_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkxNzYzODgwNw==&amp;mid=2247494801&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=ed959f838f6d1acd18d455adacdb17d6&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"进化版卡通动漫英语单词卡，提示词模板安排上了。\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">进化版卡通动漫英语单词卡，提示词模板安排上了。</a></span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link mp_article_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkxNzYzODgwNw==&amp;mid=2247491469&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=45a813dc993af9d0c74c5e523a013280&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"Lovart 加 Nano Banana 无脑批量制作知识卡片海报，我把 Lovart 做设计玩出新花样了。\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">Lovart 加 Nano Banana 无脑批量制作知识卡片海报，我把 Lovart 做设计玩出新花样了。</a></span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link mp_article_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkxNzYzODgwNw==&amp;mid=2247492503&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=d70f0fc35b1dcdc974aff29864fa96d4&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"厌倦反复重复提示词？飞书多维表格×即梦4.0助你效率翻倍！\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">厌倦反复重复提示词？飞书多维表格×即梦4.0助你效率翻倍！</a></span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link mp_article_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkxNzYzODgwNw==&amp;mid=2247490640&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=1e394e967f80aedc70a2aba628253083&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\"