-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 92, 212);box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">视频方向：</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\">海螺、Vidu、Sora 2</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 92, 212);box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">视频Agent：</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\">Medeo、Seko、OiiOii、纳米AI</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 92, 212);box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">音乐方向：</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\">Suno</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 92, 212);box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">音乐Agent：</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\">Tunee</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 92, 212);box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">配音方向：</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\">剪映、Minimax、Indextts</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 92, 212);box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">节点式工作流：</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\">ComfyUI、OpenCreator</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 92, 212);box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">开发编程：</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\">Cursor、Lovable、秒哒</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-si